# Rama Exam System

**RAMA SDA JUNIOR SCHOOL - Exam and Report System**

This is the official exam reporting system for Rama SDA Junior School, Cheptais.

## 🔹 Features:
- Admin dashboard
- Teacher marks entry
- Student performance analysis
- Report card generation
- Parent portal
- Firebase backend integration

## 🔹 How to Use:
- Visit: [Live Site](https://jestine-exam-app.github.io/rama-exam-system/)
- Log in as teacher or admin using your assigned credentials

## 🔹 Deployment:
Hosted via GitHub Pages  
Firebase handles data storage and auth

